15:58.458 --> 16:01.793
Wine court is modeled after
the quirky French legal system.

16:01.869 --> 16:05.037
It's based on every defendant's
right to a certain,

16:05.114 --> 16:06.872
mm... je ne sais quoi.

16:06.949 --> 16:08.967
How do you know about all this?

16:09.043 --> 16:12.453
Oh, Wine Court TV plays all day
in most gay bars.

16:12.530 --> 16:15.956
Your Honor, this is a case
of shocking fraud

16:15.976 --> 16:18.459
perpetrated by the worst kind
of scammers.

16:18.478 --> 16:20.870
Do we seriously believe
that a wine

16:20.888 --> 16:22.480
owned by Napoleon was found

16:22.482 --> 16:26.058
by an executive assistant
and a homemaker?

16:26.152 --> 16:29.212
They're simple,
ignorant Philistines.

16:29.214 --> 16:31.155
Mrs. Simpson,
please tell the court

16:31.232 --> 16:32.991
your recipe for sangria.

16:33.067 --> 16:34.325
Two parts Duff wine cooler

16:34.435 --> 16:37.311
to one part grape popsicle.

16:37.388 --> 16:39.980
-[all gasp]
-Oh, no, Marge.

16:40.000 --> 16:41.574
You stupid lady.

16:42.610 --> 16:45.003
Homie, I might be
going to jail for years.

16:45.005 --> 16:47.672
Promise me you'll take
good care of the kids.

16:47.823 --> 16:51.092
Honey, you know
I can't make that promise.

16:54.330 --> 16:58.224
I wonder if Homer
is looking at the same moon.

17:01.670 --> 17:02.595
[shatters]

17:02.671 --> 17:04.247
Marge was always here...

17:04.265 --> 17:07.083
[crying] to dry and put away.

17:07.085 --> 17:10.344
-[shatters]
-This is all my fault.

