17:30.275 --> 17:33.459
Kids, your mom's
not in Santa Barbara.

17:33.536 --> 17:34.552
She's in wine jail.

17:34.703 --> 17:37.371
There's no such thing
as Santa Barbara.

17:37.390 --> 17:40.449
Dad, you got to find a way
to get Mom out of jail.

17:40.451 --> 17:42.118
You got to cover this up.

17:42.136 --> 17:43.469
It's the only thing
you're good at.

17:43.621 --> 17:46.806
No, the only thing
I'm good at is nothing.

17:46.958 --> 17:49.650
I will never cover up again.

17:52.814 --> 17:54.130
Ladies, gentlemen,

17:54.148 --> 17:56.557
and bored looking cat
in a turtleneck.

17:56.634 --> 17:58.150
[purring]

17:58.227 --> 18:00.361
The wine we're accused of faking

18:00.471 --> 18:02.321
tastes exactly like
the real thing,

18:02.473 --> 18:04.898
so if-if no one
can tell the difference,

18:04.918 --> 18:06.475
how is that a crime?

18:06.494 --> 18:08.160
[all murmuring]

18:08.237 --> 18:11.330
Your Honor,
this is a case with legs.

18:11.482 --> 18:14.483
Pun intended on "legs"
but not on "case."

18:14.485 --> 18:17.095
Wine is much more
than a beverage.

18:17.246 --> 18:20.247
For centuries, it has told
the story of civilization.

18:20.266 --> 18:23.342
Whenever something is that rare,
unique, and beautiful,

18:23.494 --> 18:27.087
it is attacked by greed
and fraud at every turn.

18:27.107 --> 18:30.166
Thus, it is our responsibility

18:30.168 --> 18:33.093
to ensure that this
jewel of our society

18:33.095 --> 18:35.613
keeps its integrity intact.

18:35.764 --> 18:37.231
[meows]

18:37.342 --> 18:39.342
I have reached a decision.

18:39.360 --> 18:40.434
[groans]

18:41.471 --> 18:44.938
I declare the fake
wine in question to be...

18:44.940 --> 18:46.124
real.

18:46.275 --> 18:48.709
-Case dismissed.
-[all gasp]

18:53.358 --> 18:54.857
I don't know what just happened.

18:54.876 --> 18:56.525
Oh, allow me to explain.

18:56.544 --> 18:59.786
I bought something more valuable
than any bottle of wine:

18:59.864 --> 19:00.863
the judge.

19:00.882 --> 19:02.548
You bribed her to save us?

19:02.625 --> 19:04.475
[chuckles] I...
I wasn't saving you, Smithers,

19:04.627 --> 19:06.218
and, uh, your wife.

19:06.295 --> 19:07.979
I was protecting the myth
that the possessions

19:08.055 --> 19:10.648
