might look to fine art

19:14.970 --> 19:15.987
such as my Vermeer,

19:16.063 --> 19:18.138
Girl with a Pearl Nose Ring.

19:18.158 --> 19:21.159
<i> Or my Bible signed by Jesus.</i>

19:21.310 --> 19:23.386
And it's all thanks
to this fine fellow

19:23.404 --> 19:25.388
who alerted me
to your predicament.

19:25.406 --> 19:27.814
-Homer, you--
-Covered it up.

19:27.892 --> 19:31.410
But, Dad, you said you were
never gonna cover up again.

19:31.562 --> 19:34.397
I tried not to,
but covering up is all I know.

19:34.415 --> 19:36.582
So, I went to
the king of cover-ups.

19:36.734 --> 19:39.068
Who do you think
hid all that nuclear waste

19:39.086 --> 19:41.237
under Denver's airport?

19:41.239 --> 19:43.723
-This guy.
-[laughing] Oh, you.

19:46.519 --> 19:48.744
Great, we were saved
by an evil deed

19:48.746 --> 19:52.248
from the man whose evil deeds
we were trying to un-evil.

19:52.266 --> 19:54.525
But, Waylon,
our whole drunken plan

19:54.602 --> 19:57.695
